title: Nubar 2010 G188
description: nubar celebrates ten years of creating safe and innovative nail lacquers free of DBP (phthalate), formaldehyde, and toluene with nubar 2010. This fantastic shade consists of flakes of reflective glitter in a polychromatic base, and displays its many shades when worn alone as a sheer polish or layered over other nubar nail lacquers for a dramatic effect. The limit to nubar 2010's possibilities is your imagination!

title: OPI Nail Lacquer, Take the Stage, 0.5-Fluid Ounce
OPI Soft Shades Nail Lacquer, Princesses Rule!
description: A light, baby pink sheer polish with glitter. This shimmery pale pink shade is a versatile addition to any nail polish collection. Use a single coat on bare nails for a natural, feminine look or wear atop other polishes for a glittery pink finish. You can also layer Princesses Rule. by itself for increased opacity. The lovely, soft pink sparkle works well on all complexions. From the OPI Princesses Charming Collection.

title: Nubar Sparkles Collection - Fire Sparkle (G181)
description: G181 Fire Sparkle is a bright, fire red glitter in a red tinted base

title: OPI DS041 Bold Nail Polish, 0.5 Fluid Ounce
description: A brilliant sparkle of rich, simmering red. Borders along the shades of pink and coral. The inclusion of little white glitter specs adds greater depth without drowning the sparkle. From the Designer Series Collection.
